  <text>
  <body>
    <div>
    <head>SCENA ULTIMA.</head>
    <sp>
        <speaker><persName xml:id="Gilberto"><forename>GIL.</forename></persName></speaker>
        <l>
         Venite : è lei… <persName xml:id="Everardo"><forename>Everardo</forename></persName> <stage>(ad. <persName corresp="Everardo"><forename>Eve</forename></persName>)</stage>
        </l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
        <speaker><persName corresp="Everardo"><forename>EVE.</forename></persName></speaker>
        <l>
         Che veggo!
        </l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
        <speaker><persName corresp="Gilberto"><forename>GIL.</forename></persName></speaker>
        <l>
         <persName xml:id="Elda"><forename>Elda...</forename></persName>
        </l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
        <speaker><persName corresp="Everardo"><forename>EVE.</forename></persName></speaker>
        <l>
         Silenzio!...È spenta <stage>(coprendola della <rs type="coreference"><ref target="#Everardo"/>sua</rs> veste)</stage>
        </l>
        <l>
          Un infelice uscìa di questa vita: <stage>(ai Tem.)</stage>
        </l>
        <l>
          Per lui pregate, miei fratelli, Iddio! <stage>(tutti i <roleName>Templari</roleName> s’inginocchiano)</stage>
        </l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
        <speaker><persName corresp="Gilberto"><forename>GIL.</forename></persName></speaker>
        <l>
         Spento sarò col nuovo giorno anch’io.
        </l>
    </sp>
    <stage>
    <l>FINE</l>
    </stage>
